title: Civil rights leader, journalist Jerry Mondesire dies at 65
text:
Published By: CBS News: U.S. - Today 
J. Whyatt "Jerry" Mondesire was the longtime leader of Philadelphia's NAACP, and publisher of the Philadelphia Sunday Sun...
